ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 156 - (New Brunswick) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 156 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of NEW BRUNSWICK with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING along Saint John River affecting Victoria County from March 23 to 25, 2012.
